{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"54c762d399","title":"给宋子文的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"158e1ca6af","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":14,"articleId":"54c762d399"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji1","name":"毛泽东文集第一卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji1":{"comments":[{"id":"32c8c16ba9","publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"宋子文（一八九四——一九七一），广东文昌（今属海南省）人，国民党英美派代表。当时任国民党政府全国经济委员会主席、中国银行董事长。"},{"id":"0fa9fcb5be","publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399","index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":30,"text":"董健吾（一八九二——一九七○），江苏青浦（今属上海市）人。当时是中国共产党党员，公开身份是牧师，在上海等地从事秘密工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9996da7176","type":"title","text":"给宋子文的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"},{"id":"32c8c16ba9","type":"appellation","text":"子文先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"},{"id":"0fa9fcb5be","type":"paragraph","text":"十年分袂，国事全非，救亡图存，惟有复归于联合战线。前次董健吾兄来，托致鄙意，不知已达左右否？弟等频年三呼吁，希望南京当局改变其对外对内方针，目前虽有若干端倪，然大端仍旧不变，甚难于真正之联合抗日。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"},{"id":"3748aa4235","type":"paragraph","text":"先生邦国闻人，时有抗日绪论，甚佩甚佩！深望竿头更进，起为首倡，排斥卖国贼汉奸，恢复贵党一九二七年以前孙中山先生之革命精神，实行联俄联共农工三大政策，则非惟救国，亦以自救。寇深祸亟，情切嘤鸣，风雨同舟，愿闻明教。匆此布臆，不尽欲言！顺颂公绥","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"},{"id":"2996a5567e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"},{"id":"23ba4dadee","type":"paragraph","text":"一九三六年八月十四日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"},{"id":"7740138bab","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"},{"id":"b2fc4212de","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399"}],"page":{"id":"58fde6445b","publicationId":"wenji1","articleId":"54c762d399","start":433,"end":433}}}},"__N_SSG":true}